channel.title: How do i change port, edit title and logout
channel.description:
Hello, i run the server Ownage PK and it runs on port 666... I want to change that. how do i do it? When it runs at the top it says Ownage Pk Players Online: how do i change what it says? When i hit logout it says leave ownage pk by lothy and stuff.. I want to know how i change all that..
Thanks, Runeblade912[br][size=1]Posted on: January 30, 2007, 04:36:11 PM[/size][hr]Umm plz tell me!!!!

item.title: How do i change port, edit title and logout
item.dc:creator: @motoxman motoxman
item.description:
@motoxman wrote:

For the port , just go in server.java, and search for 666. Replace this for the new port you want ( Normally 43594 ). Compile and Run =). For the other things, just search for the source’s name and change it for you server name … Compile and run … Good luck ! Hope I helped you
